<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UG Reg Sem 1 (2025-2029) Admission Form</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha256-2XFplPlrFClt0bIdPgpz8H7ojnk10H69xRqd9+uTShA=" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'>

    <style>
        body {
            /* width: 100vw; */
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #eee;
        }

        .card {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-width: 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            background-color: #fff;
            background-clip: border-box;
        }

        .card-body {
            min-height: 1060px;
            border: 0.5px solid black;
        }

        .form-title h2 {
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .studentInfo {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 7px;
        }

        .studentInfoData {
            width: 80%;
        }

        .studentInfoPicture {
            width: 20%;
        }

        .studentInfoDataUpper .fields {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .studentInfoDataUpper .fields .fieldsName {
            width: 33%;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .studentInfoDataUpper .fields .fieldsNameValue {
            width: 67%;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding-left: 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .studentInfoDataLower {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .lowerCol1 {
            width: 30%;
        }

        .lowerCol2 {
            width: 40%;
        }

        .lowerCol3 {
            width: 30%;
        }

        .studentInfoDataLower .lowerFieldNameValue {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding-left: 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .studentInfoPicture .studentPhoto {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .studentInfoPicture img {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .studentSign {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            /* overflow: hidden; */
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .studentSign img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .addressUpper {
            display: flex;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .addressUpper .address {
            display: flex;
            width: 70%;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .addressUpper .district {
            display: flex;
            width: 30%;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .addressUpper .addressInputBox {
            width: 100%;
            height: 29px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding-left: 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .coursePaper {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .coursePaper .coursePaperLeft {
            width: 50%;
        }

        .coursePaper .coursePaperRight {
            width: 50%;
        }

        .coursePaper .paperBox {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .paperBox .paper {
            width: 22%;
        }

        .paperBox .paperName {
            width: 77%;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        .lastExamPassedRow {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .lastExamPassedRow .lastExamPassedCol {
            width: 25%;
        }

        .lastExamPassedRow .inputField {
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        .officeUseBox {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .div1 {
            width: 27%;
        }

        .div2 {
            width: 27%;
        }

        .div3 {
            width: 28%;
        }

        .div1 {
            width: 18%;
        }

        .studentAndParentSign {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .formHead h2 {
            font-size: 25px;
        }

        .formHead h6 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .note {
            color: red;
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin: 0.7cm;
            }

            .note {
                display: none;
            }

            body {
                margin-top: 0;
            }

            .card {
                width: 100vw;
            }

            .myCont {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                width: 100vw;
            }

            .formHead h2 {
                font-size: 25px;
            }

            .formHead h6 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .formHead h3 {
                font-size: 18px;
                padding-bottom: 0px;
            }

            .formHead div {
                font-size: 18px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .studentInfo {
                padding-top: 15px;
            }

            .studentInfoDataUpper div {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .studentInfoDataLower {
                padding-top: 7px;
            }

            .studentInfoDataLower div {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .studentPhoto img {
                height: 150px;
                object-fit: cover;
                object-position: center;
            }

            .studentSign {
                width: 100%;
                height: 70px;
                /* overflow: hidden; */
                /* object-fit: contain; */
            }

            .studentSign img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: contain;
                object-position: left;
            }

            .addressInfo {
                padding-top: 7px;
            }

            .addressInfo p {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .addressInfo .addressInputBox {
                font-size: 12px;
                height: 24px;
            }

            .courseDetail div {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .courseDetail p {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .lastExamPassed {
                padding-top: 7px;
            }

            .lastExamPassed div {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .lastExamPassed p {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .officeUse {
                padding-top: 7px;
            }

            .officeUse div {
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .officeUse p {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            hr {
                display: none;
            }

            .declaration {
                padding-top: 10px;
            }

            .declaration p {
                font-size: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container myCont">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class=" d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <img src="/images/sggscollegelogo-favicon.png" width="70px" alt="Logo">
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-muted text-center formHead">
                                <h2>SGGS COLLEGE, Patna City</h2>
                                <h6>ADMISSION FORM -
                                    <% if (locals.existingStudent) { %>
                                        <% if (locals.existingStudent.course==="Bachelor of Arts (Social Science Subjects)" ) { %>
                                            B.A Social Sc. (<%= locals.existingStudent.majorSubject %>) Sem - 1
                                                <% } else if
                                                    (locals.existingStudent.course==="Bachelor of Arts (Humanities Subjects)" ) {
                                                    %>
                                                    B.A Humanities (<%= locals.existingStudent.majorSubject %>) Sem - 1
                                                        <% } else { %>
                                                            B.Sc. (<%= locals.existingStudent.majorSubject %>) Sem - 1
                                                                <% } %>
                                                                    <% } %>
                                </h6>
                                <h3>SESSION 2025-29, College Roll No: <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.collegeRollNo.replace(/^\D+/g, '') %>
                                </h3>
                                <div><b>Admission Form Copy</b></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <img src="/images/ppuLogo.png" width="70px" alt="Logo">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr>

                        <!-- student info -->
                        <div class="studentInfo">
                            <div class="studentInfoData">
                                <!-- Student Upper -->
                                <div class="studentInfoDataUpper">
                                    <div class="fields">
                                        <div class="fieldsName">1. Student's Name :</div>
                                        <div class="fieldsNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.studentName %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="fields">
                                        <div class="fieldsName">2. Father's Name :</div>
                                        <div class="fieldsNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.fatherName %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="fields">
                                        <div class="fieldsName">3. Mother's Name :</div>
                                        <div class="fieldsNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.motherName %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="fields">
                                        <div class="fieldsName">4. Guardian's Name :</div>
                                        <div class="fieldsNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.guardianName %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Student Lower -->
                                <div class="studentInfoDataLower">
                                    <div class="lowerCol1">
                                        <div>Date of Birth :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.dOB %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Religion :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.religion %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Blood Group :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.bloodGroup %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Mobile No:</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.mobileNumber %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="lowerCol2">
                                        <div>Gender :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.gender %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Category :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.category %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Physically Challenge :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.physicallyChallenged %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>E-mail Id :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.email %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="lowerCol3">
                                        <div>College Roll Number </div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.collegeRollNo.replace(/^\D+/g, '') %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Marital Status :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.maritalStatus %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>Aadhar No:</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.aadharNumber %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>WhatsApp No :</div>
                                        <div class="lowerFieldNameValue">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.whatsAppNumber %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="studentInfoPicture">
                                <div class="studentPhoto">
                                    <img src="<%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.studentPhoto %>"
                                    alt="Student Photo">
                                </div>
                                <div class="studentSign">
                                    <img src="<%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.studentSign %>"
                                    alt="Student Sign">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <hr>

                        <!-- Address -->
                        <div class="addressInfo">
                            <p><b>5. Address for Correspondence</b></p>
                            <div class="addressUpper">
                                <div class="address">
                                    <p>Address</p>
                                    <div class="addressInputBox">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.address %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="district">
                                    <p>District</p>
                                    <div class="addressInputBox">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.district %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="addressUpper">
                                <div class="address">
                                    <p>PoliceStation</p>
                                    <div class="addressInputBox">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.policeStation %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="district">
                                    <p>State</p>
                                    <div class="addressInputBox">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.state %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="district">
                                    <p>PIN </p>
                                    <div class="addressInputBox">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.pinCode %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <hr>
                        <!-- course detail -->
                        <div class="courseDetail">
                            <p><b>6. Course Details</b></p>
                            <div class="coursePaper">
                                <div class="coursePaperLeft">
                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 1:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper1 %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 3:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper3 %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 5:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper5 %></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="coursePaperRight">
                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 2:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName">
                                            <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper2 %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 4:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper4 %></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="paperBox">
                                        <div class="paper">Paper - 6:</div>
                                        <div class="paperName"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.paper6 %></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr>

                        <div class="lastExamPassed">
                            <p><b>7. Last Exam Passed</b></p>
                            <div class="lastExamPassedRow">
                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Exam Name :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.examName %></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Exam Board :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.examBoard %></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Exam Year :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.examYear %></div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Obt Marks/Grade :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField">
                                        <%# locals.appliedUser.obtMarks %>
                                    </div>
                                </div> -->

                                <!-- <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Full Marks/Grade :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField">
                                        <%# locals.appliedUser.fullMarks %>
                                    </div>
                                </div> -->

                                <!-- <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Obt % :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField">
                                        <%# locals.appliedUser.obtPercent %>
                                    </div>
                                </div> -->

                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Result :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField">
                                        <%= locals.existingStudent.sem1. examResult %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="lastExamPassedRow">

                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Obt Marks/Grade :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.obtMarks %></div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Full Marks/Grade :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.fullMarks %></div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>Obt % :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.obtPercent %></div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="lastExamPassedCol">
                                    <div>PPU Confidential No :</div>
                                    <div class="inputField"><%= locals.existingStudent.sem1.ppuConfidentialNumber %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <hr>

                        <div class="officeUse">
                            <p><b>8. Office Endorsement for Admission</b></p>
                            <div class="officeUseBox">
                                <div class="div1">Admission Sign of Assistant :</div>
                                <div class="div2">Allowed Sign Admn. In-Charge :</div>
                                <div class="div3">Not Allowed Sign Admn. In-Charge :</div>
                                <div class="div4">PRINCIPAL :</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <hr>

                        <div class="declaration">
                            <p>1. We declare that all the information which is being furnished by me at the time of
                                online admission, is true to the best of my knowledge and belief. <br>
                                2. We also declare that, if any discrepancy, forgery or wrong information arises or
                                mismatch from the original documents of me at any stage, my admission would
                                automatically be treated as cancelled. I would be solely responsible for this and the
                                college administration will have no accountability in this regard. <br>
                                3. We will not request to change subject after my admission. <br>
                                4. I shall be debarred from the filling the examinations form in case the attendance is
                                below 75%. We have read and understood it.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="studentAndParentSign">
                            <p><b>Full Signature of the Parent/Guardian</b></p>
                            <p><b>Full Signature of the Student</b></p>
                        </div>


                        <div class="d-print-none mt-4">
                            <div class="float-end">
                                <a href="javascript:window.print()" class="btn btn-success me-1"><i
                                        class="fa fa-print"></i> Adm Form</a>
                                <a href="/student/<%= courseSession %>/<%= semester %>/receiptCopy" class="btn btn-primary me-1"><i
                                        class="fa fa-print"></i> Receipt</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div><!-- end col -->
    </div>
    </div>
    <script src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js'></script>
</body>

</html>